item.dc:creator: @0wnz0r 0wnz0r
item.description:
@0wnz0r wrote:

Go to the server status page: http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php
Click on a name to look for info. You will see the name of the server, IP, port, how long it’s up and since when. Fill in the IP of the Server after where it says : ‘Server IP:’ If the port is 43594 you don’t have to change it. If it is an other port. Go to Moparscape click ‘file’ and then ‘New port’ Fill in the port!
